title: Diamond 1 Bot lane looking for Jungler ( Dynamic Queue )

embed.description: Summoner Lookup with statistics, ratings, LoLSkillScore and more for HappyEmpire, a League of Legends summoner on the Europe West region.

body:
Hello everybody!

We are currently looking for an Jungler for Season 6

About me :

I am currently Diamond 2 and i main support since season 3.
I am 16 years old.
I finished school, and just started to work !. On my free time i study for my job and ofcourse play League of Legends. I've been playing League for about 3 years now. I am a fun and calm person.
I've played in different ranked Teams, and sometimes i even coach summoners, that want to improve their Supporter role.
My goal is for next season high master tier

My main Support is{{champion:412}}  cause i like his kit, and his aggressive playstyle , but i also play champions such as{{champion:432}} {{champion:201}}  and some more.

I do have a teamspeak server where we can talk beside the game + ingame

What im expecting from you

Diamond 3+
Good Champion pool
Game Knowledge
Being able to Shotcall with me


Our English is Ok, not fluent.
Languages: German and English

See you on the Rift

HappyEmpire
